TEXAS, appellant,
v.
UNITED STATES, et al. No. 12-496. Supreme Court of the United States June 27, 2013. On appeal from the United States District Court for the District of Columbia. Judgment vacated and case remanded for further consideration in light of Shelby County v. Holder, --- U.S. ----, 133 S.Ct. 2612, ---L.Ed. ---- (2013), and the suggestion of mootness of appellees Wendy Davis, et al.
